document_data.Usages:
* The sap of an ash tree was one of the ingredients of the [[steel dragon]] [[Zundaerazylym]]'s magical mixture ''[[longbite]]''.{{Cite dragon/259/Wyrms of the North: Zundaerazylym|72}}
* ''[[The Spear of White Ash]]'' was an enchanted [[Malar]]ite [[spear]] used in [[High Hunts]]s. The aptly named polearm was made out of white ash wood.
* Some used the bark and leaves of this tree to treat fevers, inflammation, or to make laxatives.<ref>
